body_html:
I converted the MNIST images into PNGs using a script available online (which was successful--the images appeared correct) and then deleted the directories for all but 4 of it's classes (the numbers 1 through 4) to reflect the number of classes I had in my actual data. I then fed those 4 classes of PNGs into the neural network, which produced the error that I was describing in my issue.

Is there specific additional information that I could provide that could help make the bug more clear? I can provide the protobufs before and after serialization as well (to complement the one included in my bug report, which is read from the TFRecord using tf.parse_single_example)
